Support:

    jQuery 1.7+

Tips: 

    if you're using jq old version, just adjust the EventAttachment 'on' to 'live' or 'delegate' on L80 & L87

Useage:

$(selector).sway({
    tree: 'tree selector', // must be selector's parents,default is parent
    css:{
        position: 'absolute', // monkey's style
        width: 1,
        overflow: 'hidden',
        backgroundColor: '#DF0000'
    },
    gravity: 'h', // h(orizontal) or v(ertical) default is V  - optional
    banana: 'banana selector' // the monkey init on it, always like: a.selected - optional
});

Demo:
    http://coochu.com  (horizontal demo)
    http://coochu.com/recipe/630  (vertical demo)

